com.informatica.mdm.bpm.idd

Class MDMTaskRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.informatica.mdm.bpm.idd.MDMTaskRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITaskRecord

    public class MDMTaskRecord
extends Object
implements ITaskRecord
    Represents the task record that is associated with the task data for IDD. This is a key that uniquely identifies a record within MDM Hub. This can either be a rowid which is the MDM Hub's unique internal identifier or a pkey source which is the system name and the primary key of the record in the source system. This class implements the ITaskRecord interface and is used by IDD to pass task related data records to the BPM Adapter implementations for various operations.
    See Also:
    IDDTaskData, ITaskData
